headline: GNRC- Ignore Short-Term Weather Impact, Focus on Long-Term Opportunity
summary: Generac Holdings Inc. (GNRC) delivered a softer-than-expected third quarter, with revenue of $1.11 billion, down 5% year-over-year and missing estimates by about $79 million. On the surface the numbers look ugly, but the story is far less dramatic than the headlines suggest, writes Tom Hayes, editor of HedgeFundTips.
